To understand this insight further, we determine the radiative (kR) and non-radiative (kNR) rates of exciton recombination using knowledge of ϕPL\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
